  "detailed_description": "Gang Beasts is a silly multiplayer party game with surly gelatinous characters, brutal slapstick fight sequences, and absurd hazardous environments, set in the mean streets of Beef City.<br />\r\n <br />\r\nCustomise your character and fight local and online enemies in the melee game mode or fight with friends against the gangs of Beef City in the gang game mode.<br />\r\n <br />\r\nGang Beasts is made by Boneloaf, a small independent game studio making a series of experimental multiplayer party games.",
  "about_the_game": "Gang Beasts is a silly multiplayer party game with surly gelatinous characters, brutal slapstick fight sequences, and absurd hazardous environments, set in the mean streets of Beef City.<br />\r\n <br />\r\nCustomise your character and fight local and online enemies in the melee game mode or fight with friends against the gangs of Beef City in the gang game mode.<br />\r\n <br />\r\nGang Beasts is made by Boneloaf, a small independent game studio making a series of experimental multiplayer party games.",
